  "texts": [
    "Differentiated clustering parameters are applied to BND-type SVs, because no length is available as a metric to drive clustering.",
    "At the beginning of post-processing, SV candidates are generated from the final clusters resulting at the end of the last stage.",
    "Start coordinates and SV length are determined based on the median of the most common values supported by the reads.",
    "Standard deviations are calculated for the trimmed distribution of indicated SV start position and lengths.",
    "The quality value is summarized as the mean mapping quality of supporting reads."
  ],
